gwt.material.design.client.base.validator

Class ValidatorWrapper<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gwt.material.design.client.base.validator.ValidatorWrapper<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<ValidatorWrapper<T>>

    public class ValidatorWrapper<T>
extends Object
implements Comparable<ValidatorWrapper<T>>
    Wraps a validator in order to provide sorting capability.

    We sort based on priority first, then insertion order. The hashCode and equals function should prevent a set from containing 2 validators of the same type.

    Author:
    Steven Jardine
